#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.40:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Dānavagga "
msgstr "4. Giving "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 40. Duccaritavipākasutta → apāyasaṃvattanikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Duccaritavipākasutta "
msgstr "40. The Results of Misconduct "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.40:1.1"
msgid "“Pāṇātipāto, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the killing of living creatures, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

#. VAR: sabbalahuso → sabbalahusoti sabbalahuko (s-a)
msgctxt "an8.40:1.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso pāṇātipātassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa appāyukasaṃvattaniko hoti. (1) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is a short life span. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.40:2.1"
msgid "Adinnādānaṃ, bhikkhave, āsevitaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ nirayasaṃvattanikaṃ tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikaṃ pettivisayasaṃvattanikaṃ. "
msgstr "Stealing, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:2.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso adinnādānassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa bhogabyasanasaṃvattaniko hoti. (2) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is loss of wealth. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an8.40:3.1"
msgid "Kāmesumicchācāro, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "Sexual misconduct, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:3.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso kāmesumicchācārassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa sapattaverasaṃvattaniko hoti. (3) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is rivalry and enmity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an8.40:4.1"
msgid "Musāvādo, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "Lying, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:4.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso musāvādassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa abhūtabbhakkhānasaṃvattaniko hoti. (4) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is false accusations. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an8.40:5.1"
msgid "Pisuṇā, bhikkhave, vācā āsevitā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nirayasaṃvattanikā tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikā pettivisayasaṃvattanikā. "
msgstr "Divisive speech, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:5.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso pisuṇāya vācāya vipāko, manussabhūtassa mittehi bhedanasaṃvattaniko hoti. (5) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is being divided against friends. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.248, sc6
msgctxt "an8.40:6.1"
msgid "Pharusā, bhikkhave, vācā āsevitā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nirayasaṃvattanikā tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikā pettivisayasaṃvattanikā. "
msgstr "Harsh speech, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:6.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso pharusāya vācāya vipāko, manussabhūtassa amanāpasaddasaṃvattaniko hoti. (6) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is hearing disagreeable things. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an8.40:7.1"
msgid "Samphappalāpo, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "Talking nonsense, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:7.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso samphappalāpassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa anādeyyavācāsaṃvattaniko hoti. (7) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is that no-one takes what you say seriously. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an8.40:8.1"
msgid "Surāmerayapānaṃ, bhikkhave, āsevitaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ nirayasaṃvattanikaṃ tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikaṃ pettivisayasaṃvattanikaṃ. "
msgstr "Taking alcoholic drinks that cause negligence, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm. "

msgctxt "an8.40:8.2"
msgid "Yo sabbalahuso surāmerayapānassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa ummattakasaṃvattaniko hotī”ti. (8) "
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is madness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.40:8.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.40:8.4"
msgid "Dānavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an8.40:9.1"
msgid "Dve dānāni vatthuñca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.2"
msgid "khettaṃ dānūpapattiyo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.3"
msgid "Kiriyaṃ dve sappurisā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.4"
msgid "abhisando vipāko cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
